This library provides lightweight validation DSL for .NET applications,
enabling fluent, expressive validation rules with strong type safety and
zero external dependencies.

Key Components:
- Fox.ValidationKit: Core library with validation rules and fluent API
- Fox.ValidationKit.ResultKit: Integration with Fox.ResultKit for Railway Oriented Programming

